		    <title outputclass="H3_1_9" xtrf="Grey" class="- topic/title ">
			      <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">570.302</ph> Description of requirements.</title>
		    <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
			      <ol class="- topic/ol " id="d973e13">
				        <li otherprops="H5_abc"
                audience="GSAR"
                outputclass="Grey_H5_abc"
                xtrf="Grey"
                class="- topic/li ">
					          <p outputclass="H5_abc"
                  xtrf="Grey"
                  class="- topic/p "
                  id="d964e17">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						             The description of requirements depends on the nature of the space the agency needs and the market available to satisfy that need.</p>
				        </li>
				        <li otherprops="H5_abc"
                audience="GSAR"
                outputclass="Grey_H5_abc"
                xtrf="Grey"
                class="- topic/li ">
					          <p outputclass="H5_abc"
                  xtrf="Grey"
                  class="- topic/p "
                  id="d964e26">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						             The description of requirements must include all the following:</p>
					          <ol class="- topic/ol " id="d973e32">
						            <li otherprops="H6_123"
                      audience="GSAR"
                      outputclass="Grey_H6_123"
                      xtrf="Grey"
                      class="- topic/li ">
							              <p outputclass="H6_123"
                        xtrf="Grey"
                        class="- topic/p "
                        id="d964e36">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                 A statement of the purpose of the lease.</p>
						            </li>
						            <li otherprops="H6_123"
                      audience="GSAR"
                      outputclass="Grey_H6_123"
                      xtrf="Grey"
                      class="- topic/li ">
							              <p outputclass="H6_123"
                        xtrf="Grey"
                        class="- topic/p "
                        id="d964e45">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                 Functional, performance, or physical requirements.</p>
						            </li>
						            <li otherprops="H6_123"
                      audience="GSAR"
                      outputclass="Grey_H6_123"
                      xtrf="Grey"
                      class="- topic/li ">
							              <p outputclass="H6_123"
                        xtrf="Grey"
                        class="- topic/p "
                        id="d964e54">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(3)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                 Any special requirements.</p>
						            </li>
						            <li otherprops="H6_123"
                      audience="GSAR"
                      outputclass="Grey_H6_123"
                      xtrf="Grey"
                      class="- topic/li ">
							              <p outputclass="H6_123"
                        xtrf="Grey"
                        class="- topic/p "
                        id="d964e63">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(4)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                 The delivery schedule.</p>
						            </li>
					          </ol>
				        </li>
				        <li otherprops="H5_abc"
                audience="GSAR"
                outputclass="Grey_H5_abc"
                xtrf="Grey"
                class="- topic/li ">
					          <p outputclass="H5_abc"
                  xtrf="Grey"
                  class="- topic/p "
                  id="d964e74">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						             The description must promote full and open competition. Include restrictive provisions or conditions only to the extent necessary to satisfy the agency’s needs or as authorized by law.</p>
				        </li>
			      </ol>
